high_descs: turn right and walk straight then turn left and walk straight towards the fridge and turn left then turn right at the fridge
open the fridge and take the glass out and close the door
turn left and walk straight towards the sink and turn right
put the glass in the sink and fill it with water then drain the sink and remove the glass
turn around and walk straight then turn right towards the stove and look up
open the microwave and put the glass inside and close the door
anns.task_desc: clean a glass off from the fridge and put it into the microwave

high_descs: Walk around the right side of the center table to face the fridge.
Pick up the glass in the top of the fridge.
Step to the left to face the sink.
Wash the glass in the sink and remove it.
Turn left and look up to face the microwave.
Place the glass in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To wash a glass as well as place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right, hang a left at the wall and walk to the white fridge.
Pick up the clear glass from inside the fridge on the top shelf and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Place the chilled glass in the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the stove on the right.
Put the rinsed glass inside the microwave above the stove and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed glass inside a microwave.
